{"tid":506512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2百公斤男破處　嘿咻女友致腦震盪","createTime":"2017-12-22T09:39:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T15:08:34.000Z","uid":122,"like":135,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"b54e7bd32e703403d656015325c6cb654c236668","tid":506512,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T09:39:39.000Z","msg":"<strong>2百公斤男破處　嘿咻女友致腦震盪</strong><br />\n<br />\n2013/12/20 07:23<br />\n【陳亮諭／綜合報導】美國1對情侶初嘗禁果，男子卡薩羅那體重近200公斤，21歲那年決定與女友格拉卡莉絲分享自己的初夜，未料把她的頭頂撞進牆，嚇得以為撞死人，女友還問，為什麼要停；女友送醫被診斷出腦震盪。 <br />\n<br />\n今日出版的《蘋果》報導，美國《旅遊生活》頻道（TLC）將在下周六播出新節目《性愛送我掛急診》（Sex Sent Me to the ER），邀請情侶分享自己因為性愛被緊急送醫的經驗，該對情侶為該節目的首集嘉賓，也找來演員重現當時場景。"},{"pid":"183b1c216d83c2def43e9defab2528d557afca48","tid":506512,"uid":42188,"like":1019,"dislike":13,"score":1006,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T09:40:28.000Z","msg":"當年鄭少秋又有冇試過腦震盪?"},{"pid":"4c7571b4934812efa3a55e1a59f6bd203354f0de","tid":506512,"uid":6030,"like":201,"dislike":1,"score":200,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T09:44:24.000Z","msg":"哈哈哈哈哈哈⋯好野黎啦"},{"pid":"f1bff9e9e0622264d09bbf87184e546c6706c7ac","tid":506512,"uid":14918,"like":50,"dislike":2,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T10:00:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哈哈哈哈哈哈⋯好野黎啦</blockquote><br />\n點解咁好味架...正到痺呀！"},{"pid":"76123d31d0ac66eff158c226e6c3c6d76c59ca58","tid":506512,"uid":28378,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T10:16:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>哈哈哈哈哈哈⋯好野黎啦</blockquote><br />\n點解咁好味架...正到痺呀！</blockquote><br />\n無得頂啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1a09cd02b23e1797053ceb9bcc1f5fa6129fb3","tid":506512,"uid":136662,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T10:28:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>哈哈哈哈哈哈⋯好野黎啦</blockquote><br />\n點解咁好味架...正到痺呀！</blockquote><br />\n無得頂啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 